{"tid":2360685,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉淑儀：民主派人士因初選被捕是合理","createTime":"2021-01-10T04:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T05:36:56.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"465ba7e2517610c37aaf18dc95377474e92f58bb","tid":2360685,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/54de3a75be61ce3329c97acef7a135e7/2020/10/6f5f82f4ae0de656ab28cf09ac252646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F54de3a75be61ce3329c97acef7a135e7%2F2020%2F10%2F6f5f82f4ae0de656ab28cf09ac252646.jpg&h=f02fb8b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員葉劉淑儀在一個電視節目表示，上星期民主派53人因參與初選涉及「顛覆國家政權」被捕是合理，並非濫捕，相信警方仍會繼續深入調查，不相信所有被捕人士最終都會被檢控。<strong><span class=\"red\">她批評參與初選的人，不少人聲稱會否決所有政府議案，包括財政預算案，質疑他們未看過議案就要否決，決心迫行政長官下台，令社會混亂，就是犯國安法，形容行徑「惡毒」，扭曲基本法機制，任何國家都不會</span></strong>容許。 <br />\n<br />\n被問到是否意味立法會議員不能否決政府議案，葉劉淑儀認為相關權利要合理、合法行駛，舉例建制派議員即使佔議會絕大多數，很多近日的重要議案，包括「明日大嶼」、第四輪防疫抗疫基金等，有議員都投棄權票，甚至反對票，她形容這些行為與民主派有別，都是「有理據或善意」的反對，不是為了癱瘓政府，證明只要真誠擁護基本法，仍可在議會投反對票。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2374145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2374145&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDbYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=df43b7cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2374145</a>"},{"pid":"5afc1e4e76ae18559c481eff16fa16829ac11eda","tid":2360685,"uid":76804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:21:55.000Z","msg":"特朗普一落台<br />\n唔驚自己被制裁<br />\n呢幾日係咁周圍吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee9928e4bda359234cf7d86d444cf6bc4d4f551","tid":2360685,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:27:43.000Z","msg":"其實喺《国安法》下任可人未經中央許可就擅自宣佈參選行政長官呢種意圖奪權嘅行為都足以構成顛覆国家政權罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537f715758c9c3c07986c314b97c1df728108f8d","tid":2360685,"uid":145273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:29:54.000Z","msg":"咁你做得唔好,就要落台! 但係你唔肯落台,咁人地用方法逼你落台,但係你就打壓人地,<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><strong><span class=\"red\">獨裁政府</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5adb51a891570e5da58a88a34888ddf8f9fdc36f","tid":2360685,"uid":6297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:32:18.000Z","msg":"姐姐呢排行得好前，熱身了熱身了"},{"pid":"0774e36047b0761064159a6c0a4053984ad9beb4","tid":2360685,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8587e6860138bfd8c45bf8985a43944c830062ec","tid":2360685,"uid":32722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"姐姐一心想加入勝利11人，點知到左今日老美依然未得閒理佢"},{"pid":"14574bc5d49e752f3cd43d7080d294ac14082825","tid":2360685,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:53:22.000Z","msg":"成日話佢冇決策唔應該被制裁<br />\n原來係背後話事人黎架"},{"pid":"b2417d63c27581989065f0c8390eb7792d3906f3","tid":2360685,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:00:59.000Z","msg":"姐姐準備食丹麥通緝令未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99886f3996ba0db0f6aa7285c60da5342d51ecb5","tid":2360685,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:02:34.000Z","msg":"國安法同聖經一樣<br />\n係人都有罪"},{"pid":"2be7bb2431c243f3ede211f48cdbc109a9ea129b","tid":2360685,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:05:10.000Z","msg":"立法會既存在有國安漏洞<br />\n仲唔取消？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804f34e5513a7abdb673887da4f7988fe502e81f","tid":2360685,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:36:5